Package org.gvsig.fmap.core

Class Summary
FeatureUtil Class with utility methods to work with FMap features.
FGeometryUtil Utility methods to work with FMap geometries.
FLyrUtil Utility methods to work with FMap layers
MultipartShapeIterator This class is a try to give a more usable interface to FMap geometries.
NewFConverter Offers the same functionality than com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.v02.FConverter, but doesnt do some checks that FConverter does (for example, it doesnt close unclosed Polygons).
ShapePointExtractor This class receives a Shape implementation and extracts its coordinates.
 

Exception Summary
IncorrectJtsGeometryException Exception launched when we try to build a JTS geometry and JTS launchs an exception.
